N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 166.4 - Clearly show grade in advertisement with price

State Regulations

Any advertisement of potatoes for sale at a given price
shall plainly and conspicuously indicate the grade of such
potatoes. Notes
